  "body": "This happens with geth built from the branch `develop`\n\n`geth account new --datadir=/tmp` \nyields: `Incorrect Usage.` \n\n`geth account list --datadir=/tmp` \nproduces: `flag provided but not defined: -datadir`\n\nThe following part is Android related:\nWhen I do not give a datadir in:\n`Geth.run(\"account new\");`\n\nI get the following error: \n`Fatal: Cannot determine default data directory, please set manually (--datadir)`\n",
